title: Best of 2019:  Sexy And Simple Minded
itunes:title: Best of 2019:  Sexy And Simple Minded
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I'm a 29 year old man and three months ago, I started dating a gorgeous woman in her mid-twenties. She has the best body, smooth and glowy chocolate skin, the sexiest voice and she is the best that I ever had, if you know what I mean. She's very affectionate and she treats me well, but she's missing one important thing... a brain..................
